tr.td:
Note: Only the predefined date formats are garbage-free: (millisecond separator may be either
                a comma ',' or a period '.')



                    Pattern
                    Example



                    %d{DEFAULT}
                    2012-11-02 14:34:02,781



                    %d{ISO8601}
                    2012-11-02T14:34:02,781



                    %d{ISO8601_BASIC}
                    20121102T143402,781



                    %d{ABSOLUTE}
                    14:34:02,781



                    %d{DATE}
                    02 Nov 2012 14:34:02,781



                    %d{COMPACT}
                    20121102143402781



                    %d{HH:mm:ss,SSS}
                    14:34:02,781



                    %d{dd MMM yyyy HH:mm:ss,SSS}
                    02 Nov 2012 14:34:02,781



                    %d{HH:mm:ss}{GMT+0}
                    18:34:02



                    %d{UNIX}
                    1351866842



                    %d{UNIX_MILLIS}
                    1351866842781

